holy patronage so that by following your example and aided by your spiritual guidance, we may be enabled to lead a holy life, die a happy death, and come at last to the possession of everlasting blessedness in Heaven. Amen.

In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.



